Usage: chpl [flags|source files]

Compilation Traces:       default   type     description
-------------------       --------  -------  --------------------------------
      --print-passes      false     ->true   Print compiler passes
      --print-commands    false     ->true   Print system commands

Code Size Statistics:
---------------------
      --print-code-size   false     ->true   Print code size statistics
      --count-tokens      false     ->true   Count tokens

Optimization Control:
---------------------
      --no-bounds-checks  false     ->true   Disable bounds checking
      --no-inline         false     ->true   Do not inline functions
      --unoptimized       false     ->true   Generate naive code (many temps)
      --scalar-replace-tuples false     ->true   Generate scalar components of tuples
      --no-single-loop-iterator-opt false     ->true   Disable the optimization of iterators composed of a single loop
      --no-expand-iterators-inline-opt false     ->true   Disable the expansion of iterators inlined around loop bodies
      --no-copy-propagation false     ->true   Disable copy propagation

Code Generation:
----------------
      --savec                       path     Save generated C code in directory
  -g, --[no-]debug        false     ->true   Allow debugging of generated C code
  -O, --[no-]optimize     false     ->true   Optimize generated C code
      --[no-]cg-cpp-lines false     ->true   Generate #line annotations
  -p, --parallel          true      toggle   Toggle threaded code generation

Linker Control:
---------------
  -o, --output            a.out     path     Name output executable
  -L, --lib-search-path             path     C library search path
  -l, --lib-linkage                 path     C library linkage
      --ccflags                     string   Back-end C compiler flags

Miscellaneous Flags:
--------------------
      --no-warnings       false     ->true   Disable output of warnings
      --instantiate-max   256       int      Limit number of instantiations
      --chplhome          .         path     Over-ride $CHPL_HOME
      --[no-]devel        false     ->true   Compile as developer
  -s, --set                         string   Set config param value
      --explain-call                string   Explain resolution of call

Compiler Information:
---------------------
      --version                              Show Version
      --copyright                            Show Copyright
      --license                              Show License
  -h, --help                                 Help (show this list)
